ABOUT US

At Laitkor we understand the importance of design, it depicts your organization’s brand and embeds your organization’s belief, values and ideologies. We believe strongly that a good design creates a right message which helps you develop a unique brand identity and making your brand progressive and innovative.

Laitkor is a blend of people and technology. Our experienced designing team is mix of analytical, creative and technical background. We make sure all your project whether graphics , web or mobile are created with the same zest with prime focus on delivering creative and attractive solution for our clients.

Things we are good at

At Laitkor, we understand the power of a good design and the impact it can create. Every design we create makes sure that it is in sync with your brand identity and makes you stand out from competition.

We have lots of experience in graphics as well as web/mobile design and are extremely good at Photoshop, Flash, Corel Draw , Responsive Website, HTML5, CSS3, jQuery, WordPress, Joomla and similar technologies.
